### ===========================
### Trainer Expense API Tests
### ===========================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/trainer-expense
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}


### -----------------------------------------------
### Login first (to obtain accessToken)
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "kyu@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 1. Create Expense - Rent
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name createExpense
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "RENT",
    "amount": 2000000,
    "memo": "April studio rent",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 2. Create Expense - Supply
### -----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "SUPPLY",
    "amount": 150000,
    "memo": "Resistance bands and foam rollers",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-05T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 3. Create Expense - Utility
### -----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "UTILITY",
    "amount": 120000,
    "memo": "Electricity and internet bill",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-10T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 4. Get All Expenses
### -----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 5. Filter by Category
### -----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}?category=RENT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 6. Filter by Date Range
### -----------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}?start-date=2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&end-date=2026-04-05T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 7. Get Expense by ID
### -----------------------------------------------
@expenseId = {{createExpense.response.body.id}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 8. Update Expense
### -----------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 1950000,
    "memo": "April studio rent (discount applied)"
}

### -----------------------------------------------
### 9. Delete Expense
### -----------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ===========================
### Security Test Cases
### ===========================

### 10. [AuthN] Reject unauthenticated request -> 401
GET {{baseUrl}}

### 11. [Input Validation] Reject negative amount -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "RENT",
    "amount": -1000,
    "memo": "Negative amount test",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### 12. [Input Validation] Reject amount above cap -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "RENT",
    "amount": 999999999999,
    "memo": "Integer overflow test",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### 13. [Input Validation] Reject invalid category -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "INVALID_CATEGORY",
    "amount": 10000,
    "memo": "Enum injection test",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### 14. [Input Validation] Reject non-integer amount (type confusion) -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "RENT",
    "amount": 1000.999,
    "memo": "Float rounding attack test",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### 15. [BOLA] Accessing another trainer's expense returns 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/4176f0df-d796-44aa-9a07-ebdf3b85ef93
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 16. [Input Validation] Reject string amount -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "RENT",
    "amount": "2000000",
    "memo": "String-to-number coercion test",
    "paidAt": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}